verbose_text: Based on the results of significant DE-lncRNA analysis in the HT, LO and HL groups, the most significantly enriched GO terms in biological processes category were the regulation of Fc receptor mediated stimulatory signaling pathway, ribosomal large subunit biogenesis and microtubule based process; the most significantly enriched GO terms in cellular components category based on DE-lncRNAs were ribosome, preribosome and intracellular non-membrane-bounded organelle.
evidence: Fc receptor mediated stimulatory signaling pathway, ribosomal large subunit biogenesis
